<item>
            <title>[FELIX-4871] The felix framework logger can&apos;t be used with reflection anymore</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-4871</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Not being able to use reflection means you need to create a separate jar for the logger so that it can be loaded with the required framework classes.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12825490">FELIX-4871</key>
            <summary>The felix framework logger can&apos;t be used with reflection anymore</summary>
